OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FA woman whose mother died after
OL,8,Fcontracting Covid in hospital has told
OL,9,Fthe in Wales that the Welsh Government
OL,10,F"sat on their hands" when they
OL,11,Frealised the impact of the virus.
OL,13,FThe inquiry continued on Wednesday
OL,14,Fmorning with bereaved families giving
OL,15,Fevidence.
OL,17,FElizabeth Grant, a founding member of
OL,18,FCovid Bereaved Families for Justice
OL,19,FCymru, gave evidence at the inquiry.
OL,20,FHer mother died in April 2020 after
OL,21,Ftesting positive for Covid.
