OL,7,FElizabeth's mother had been admitted
OL,8,Fto hospital after falling and breaking
OL,9,Fher hip. She had an operation and was
OL,10,Fthen moved to a community hospital.
OL,12,FElizabeth said she was not aware of
OL,13,Fthe use of personal protective
OL,14,Fequipment (PPE) at the hospital, and
OL,15,Fher mother was not tested for Covid on
OL,16,Fadmission or when she was discharged
OL,17,Ffrom the previous hospital she was in.
