OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAt the time of her mother's death,
OL,8,Ffunerals were limited to 10 people.
OL,9,FElizabeth said no one attended her
OL,10,Fmother's as they could not decide who
OL,11,Fwould go.
OL,13,FSpeaking of the members of the
OL,14,Fbereavement group, she said: "We have
OL,15,Fover 400 members and not one person's
OL,16,Fbeen offered bereavement support."
