OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FElizabeth, who lived in Bath during
OL,8,Fthe pandemic, said the differences in
OL,9,Frules between England and Wales were
OL,10,F"tantamount to chaos," adding that "it
OL,11,Fwas very difficult to get, when you
OL,12,Fwere in England, any information of
OL,13,Fwhat was happening in Wales."
OL,15,FThe UK Government advised the public
OL,16,Fon 11 May 2020 to consider wearing
OL,17,Fface masks in enclosed public spaces.
OL,18,FSoon after this became mandatory.
