OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FIt was not until 11 September 2020
OL,8,Fthat all in Wales were required to
OL,9,Fwear masks in public indoor spaces.
OL,11,FAfter watching Tuesday's opening of
OL,12,Fthe inquiry in Wales, Elizabeth said:
OL,13,F"It does sound like they were caught
OL,14,Fwith their trousers down and when they
OL,15,Frealised the impact of the virus on
OL,16,FWelsh shores they sat on their hands."
