OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAmanda Provis's mother and grandmother
OL,8,Fboth died of Covid. She told the
OL,9,Finquiry that her father, who worked as
OL,10,Fa hospital porter throughout the
OL,11,Fpandemic, was provided with "nothing
OL,12,Fat all" in relation to PPE at the
OL,13,Fstart of the pandemic.
OL,15,FShe said he began to show symptoms of
OL,16,FCovid at the end of March 2020 and was
OL,17,Ftold to go home from work and self-
OL,18,Fisolate, and he slept in a separate
OL,19,Froom to his wife.
