OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAmanda said her mother started to show
OL,8,Fsymptoms a day or so later. She
OL,9,Fbelieves her father caught coronavirus
OL,10,Fat work and passed it on to her mother.
OL,12,FShe said her father's PCR test came
OL,13,Fback positive on 6 April 2020 the same
OL,14,Fday her mother's symptoms worsened.
OL,15,FHer mother died the next day.
