OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAmanda's mother had been advised by a
OL,8,Fdoctor over the phone to use a rescue
OL,9,Fpack for her pre-existing COPD, which
OL,10,Fcontained antibiotics, an asthma pump
OL,11,Fand steroids, which she started
OL,12,Fstraight away, the inquiry was told.
OL,14,FShe said her mother was not advised to
OL,15,Fgo to hospital at any stage.
OL,17,FThe inquiry and will hear from a range
OL,18,Fof groups, including representatives
OL,19,Fof bereaved families, unions, care
OL,20,Fhomes, and the Welsh Government.
