OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FOn Wednesday it also heard from
OL,8,FProfessor Debbie Foster, a Cardiff
OL,9,FUniversity academic, who was involved
OL,10,Fin writing a report investigating the
OL,11,Fimpact of the pandemic on disabled
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FProfessor Foster told the inquiry that
OL,15,Fthe Welsh Government responded "very
OL,16,Fslowly" to concerns raised, including
OL,17,Faccess to services, people being
OL,18,Fneglected and people being at risk of
OL,19,Fabuse.
