OL,3,CThe heartbreaking testimonies of
OL,4,Cbereaved families at Covid Inquiry in
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FEvidence shows disabled people were
OL,8,Fdisproportionately more likely to die
OL,9,Fof Covid.
OL,11,FShe also said "to be quite honest we
OL,12,Fthought we'd been forgotten
OL,13,Fcompletely" while waiting to meet with
OL,14,Fthe Welsh Government after finishing
OL,15,Fthe report, and she felt the report
OL,16,Fwas not published quickly enough by
OL,17,Fthe government.
OL,19,FWelsh Government officials and
OL,20,Fministers are due to be questioned by
OL,21,Fthe inquiry from next week.
